{"title":"将军山","authors":["李磊"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":3,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李磊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你最高的山顶上  　找不到将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军只是一棵普通的树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山坡上摇曳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使他更接近大地的心脏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军倒下的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峰一阵摇晃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风把石头和花草吹来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大别山无数峰峦中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军是最高的一座"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他高耸的额头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁着大别山的梦想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他深邃的眼睛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日夜把田野眺望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他嘴唇沉默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛在倾听母亲的话语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他岿然不动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如士兵守护着故乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许将军的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然流动着战火的硝烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但和平已使枪管冷却"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的花朵遍山开放"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或许将军的心中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依然深藏着贫穷的忧伤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但丰收已扛在农民肩头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一碗老米酒温热将军的柔肠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最高的山顶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"找不到将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军只是一块平凡的石头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺在肥沃的泥土上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使大别山更稳固地走向太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将军因山而永恒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山因将军而辉煌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}